snippet.title: Rival Turf! - SNES Gameplay
snippet.description:
The original SNES gameplay archive, est 2008 includes gameplay captures from SOME commercial releases from the US market.

As of Dec 2024, I've resumed efforts to start capturing gameplay again. Some of these efforts are being streamed on Twitch, and text updates will be posted to BlueSky (which doesn't require an account to view). Please follow these if you're interested!

https://bsky.app/profile/nesguide.com
https://twitch.tv/nesguide
